MBOMBELA &#8211; The latest addition to Ho rskool Bergvlam&#8217;s technology offering will give pupils the opportunity to gain electrical-engineering qualifications up to an NQF3 level. Bergvlam is the only high school in Mbombela that offers a technical line. The new three-phase motor test board was installed in the electrical-technology class during the winter holidays. It is used with the assistance of teacher, Hannes Beeslaar.